# MCP Gateway secrets — copy to /opt/seshat/mcp-secrets.env on VPS host (never commit).
# docker/mcp-gateway reads this file to inject credentials into MCP server containers.
# See: docker/mcp/run-gateway.sh
#
# NOTE: LINEAR_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN is kept here for documentation but is NOT used
# by the current gateway setup.  docker/mcp-gateway routes linear through Docker
# Desktop OAuth (DCR) which is unavailable on a plain VPS.  Linear MCP requires
# a separate integration (future work).  The gateway currently runs:
#   sequentialthinking, context7   (no credentials required)
